OL,3,CAndy Burnham to set out economic
OL,4,Cvision in first major speech of
OL,5,Cleadership bid
OL,7,FAndy Burnham is expected to set out
OL,8,Fhis economic agenda on Monday in his
OL,9,Ffirst major speech since announcing he
OL,10,Fwould stand for the Labour leadership.
OL,12,FReports suggests the former Greater
OL,13,FManchester mayor will use his speech
OL,14,Fto argue for a radical devolution of
OL,15,Fpower and money away from Whitehall.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
