OL,3,CAndy Burnham to set out economic
OL,4,Cvision in first major speech of
OL,5,Cleadership bid
OL,7,FA long-standing proponent of
OL,8,Fdevolution, Mr Burnham will set out
OL,9,Fplans to boost economic growth by
OL,10,Fgiving regional mayors more control
OL,11,Fover social housing, welfare and post-
OL,12,F16 education, according to The Times.
OL,14,FSuch an agenda would be in line with
OL,15,Fthe views he set out in his book, Head
OL,16,FNorth, alongside his friend and fellow
OL,17,Fmayor Steve Rotheram.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
