OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782551897
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to set out economic
OL,4,Cvision in first major speech of
OL,5,Cleadership bid
OL,7,FIn the book, Mr Burnham said the
OL,8,Fcurrent system saw regional leaders
OL,9,Fgoing "on bended knee" to Westminster
OL,10,Fand called for a "more balanced
OL,11,Fapproach, where councils and mayors
OL,12,Fwere dealt some cards too".
OL,14,FIf Mr Burnham remains the only
OL,15,Fcandidate for the Labour leadership,
OL,16,Fhis speech will come exactly three
OL,17,Fweeks before he enters Downing Street.
OL,26,@qD@GOUqD@VO]rD@ROUtD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
