OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782551897
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to set out economic
OL,4,Cvision in first major speech of
OL,5,Cleadership bid
OL,7,FNominations for the leadership close
OL,8,Fon July 16, and if Mr Burnham is the
OL,9,Fonly candidate he will be formally
OL,10,Fdeclared Labour leader at a special
OL,11,Fconference the following day.
OL,13,FBut precedent states he will not
OL,14,Fbecome prime minister immediately,
OL,15,Fwith the handover taking place on the
OL,16,Fnext working day, July 20.
OL,18,FMeanwhile, Mr Burnham continues to
OL,19,Fmull his future cabinet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
